{
  "video_id": "28sa2zGgmwE",
  "title": "How Africa can use its traditional knowledge to make progress | Chika Ezeanya-Esiobu",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13540.0,
      "end_time": 18534.0,
      "text": "Some months back, I was visiting this East African city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18558.0,
      "end_time": 21547.0,
      "text": "and we were stuck in traffic."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21571.0,
      "end_time": 24613.0,
      "text": "And this vendor suddenly approaches my window"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24637.0,
      "end_time": 27180.0,
      "text": "with a half-opened alphabet sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28505.0,
      "end_time": 31323.0,
      "text": "I took a quick look at the alphabet sheet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31348.0,
      "end_time": 32783.0,
      "text": "and I thought of my daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32807.0,
      "end_time": 35369.0,
      "text": "how it would be nice to spread it on the floor"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35393.0,
      "end_time": 37233.0,
      "text": "and just play all over it with her"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37257.0,
      "end_time": 39446.0,
      "text": "while getting her to learn the alphabet."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39470.0,
      "end_time": 42765.0,
      "text": "So the traffic moved a bit, and I quickly grabbed a copy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42789.0,
      "end_time": 44788.0,
      "text": "and we moved on."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46165.0,
      "end_time": 49266.0,
      "text": "When I had time to fully open the alphabet sheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49290.0,
      "end_time": 51619.0,
      "text": "and take a more detailed look at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51643.0,
      "end_time": 54666.0,
      "text": "I knew I was not going to use that to teach my daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55267.0,
      "end_time": 56784.0,
      "text": "I regretted my purchase."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58331.0,
      "end_time": 59673.0,
      "text": "Why so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60338.0,
      "end_time": 63124.0,
      "text": "Looking at the alphabet sheet reminded me of the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63148.0,
      "end_time": 65524.0,
      "text": "that not much has changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65548.0,
      "end_time": 67971.0,
      "text": "in the education curricula in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68729.0,
      "end_time": 72449.0,
      "text": "Some decades back, I was taught out of a similar alphabet sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73312.0,
      "end_time": 75569.0,
      "text": "And because of that, I struggled for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76464.0,
      "end_time": 80960.0,
      "text": "I struggled to reconcile my reality with the formal education I received"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80984.0,
      "end_time": 83131.0,
      "text": "in school, in the schools I attended."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84592.0,
      "end_time": 86602.0,
      "text": "I had identity crises."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86626.0,
      "end_time": 89535.0,
      "text": "I looked down on my reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89559.0,
      "end_time": 93804.0,
      "text": "I looked at my ancestry, I looked at my lineage with disrespect."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94205.0,
      "end_time": 99258.0,
      "text": "I had very little patience for what my life had to offer around me."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101450.0,
      "end_time": 102444.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103496.0,
      "end_time": 104914.0,
      "text": "\"A is for apple.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106421.0,
      "end_time": 107845.0,
      "text": "\"A is for apple.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109528.0,
      "end_time": 114216.0,
      "text": "\"A is for apple\" is for that child in that part of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114240.0,
      "end_time": 115972.0,
      "text": "where apples grow out;"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116751.0,
      "end_time": 118727.0,
      "text": "who has an apple in her lunch bag;"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120235.0,
      "end_time": 123637.0,
      "text": "who goes to the grocery store with her mom and sees red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123661.0,
      "end_time": 127314.0,
      "text": "green, yellow -- apples of all shapes and colors and sizes."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128490.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130938.00000000001,
      "text": "And so, introducing education to this child"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130961.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133840.0,
      "text": "with an alphabet sheet like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134900.0,
      "end_time": 137131.0,
      "text": "fulfills one of the major functions of education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137155.0,
      "end_time": 140317.0,
      "text": "which is to introduce the learner"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140341.0,
      "end_time": 143714.0,
      "text": "to an appreciation of the learner&#39;s environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143738.0,
      "end_time": 148380.0,
      "text": "and a curiosity to explore more in order to add value."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 149581.0,
      "end_time": 150992.0,
      "text": "In my own case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152140.0,
      "end_time": 154326.0,
      "text": "when and where I grew up in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155613.0,
      "end_time": 157443.0,
      "text": "apple was an exotic fruit."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 158719.0,
      "end_time": 160103.0,
      "text": "Two or three times a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160128.0,
      "end_time": 165494.0,
      "text": "I could get some yellowish apples with brown dots, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165519.0,
      "end_time": 169416.0,
      "text": "signifying thousands of miles traveled -- warehouses storing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 169440.0,
      "end_time": 170614.0,
      "text": "to get to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171575.0,
      "end_time": 173486.0,
      "text": "I grew up in the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173510.0,
      "end_time": 176510.0,
      "text": "to very financially comfortable parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176534.0,
      "end_time": 178476.0,
      "text": "so it was my dignified reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178500.0,
      "end_time": 180811.0,
      "text": "exactly the same way"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180835.0,
      "end_time": 184997.0,
      "text": "cassava fufu or ugali would not regularly feature"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185210.0,
      "end_time": 187922.0,
      "text": "in an American, Chinese or Indian diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188851.0,
      "end_time": 191280.0,
      "text": "apples didn&#39;t count as part of my reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192208.0,
      "end_time": 195256.0,
      "text": "So what this did to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 195280.0,
      "end_time": 198964.0,
      "text": "introducing education to me with \"A is for apple,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 198988.0,
      "end_time": 201447.0,
      "text": "made education an abstraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201914.0,
      "end_time": 203783.0,
      "text": "It made it something out of my reach --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204665.0,
      "end_time": 206571.0,
      "text": "a foreign concept,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206595.0,
      "end_time": 210401.0,
      "text": "a phenomenon for which I would have to constantly and perpetually seek"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210425.0,
      "end_time": 212236.0,
      "text": "the validation of those it belonged to"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 215200.0,
      "text": "for me to make progress within it and with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216109.0,
      "end_time": 219150.0,
      "text": "That was tough for a child; it would be tough for anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220420.0,
      "end_time": 222765.0,
      "text": "As I grew up and I advanced academically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222789.0,
      "end_time": 227852.0,
      "text": "my reality was further separated from my education."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228739.0,
      "end_time": 230485.0,
      "text": "In history, I was taught"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 230509.0,
      "end_time": 234760.0,
      "text": "that the Scottish explorer Mungo Park discovered the Niger River."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235631.0,
      "end_time": 237424.0,
      "text": "And so it bothered me."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237448.0,
      "end_time": 239463.0,
      "text": "My great-great-grandparents grew up"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239487.0,
      "end_time": 241490.0,
      "text": "quite close to the edge of the Niger River."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241514.0,
      "end_time": 243933.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243957.0,
      "end_time": 250434.0,
      "text": "And it took someone to travel thousands of miles from Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250458.0,
      "end_time": 252905.0,
      "text": "to discover a river right under their nose?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 252929.0,
      "end_time": 255370.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 255394.0,
      "end_time": 256551.0,
      "text": "No!"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 256575.0,
      "end_time": 261993.0,
      "text": "(Applause and cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 262170.0,
      "end_time": 263946.0,
      "text": "What did they do with their time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 263971.0,
      "end_time": 265868.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 265892.0,
      "end_time": 268723.0,
      "text": "Playing board games, roasting fresh yams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 268747.0,
      "end_time": 270127.0,
      "text": "fighting tribal wars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270557.0,
      "end_time": 275417.0,
      "text": "I mean, I just knew my education was preparing me to go somewhere else"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 275441.0,
      "end_time": 279207.0,
      "text": "and practice and give to another environment that it belonged to."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 279232.0,
      "end_time": 282415.0,
      "text": "It was not for my environment, where and when I grew up."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 283290.0,
      "end_time": 284188.0,
      "text": "And this continued."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284212.0,
      "end_time": 286104.0,
      "text": "This philosophy undergirded my studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 286129.0,
      "end_time": 288594.0,
      "text": "all through the time I studied in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 288618.0,
      "end_time": 292452.0,
      "text": "It took a lot of experiences and some studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 292476.0,
      "end_time": 295628.0,
      "text": "for me to begin to have a change of mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 295652.0,
      "end_time": 298616.0,
      "text": "I will share a couple of the remarkable ones with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299735.0,
      "end_time": 302900.0,
      "text": "I was in the United States in Washington, DC"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302114.0,
      "end_time": 304155.0,
      "text": "studying towards my doctorate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304180.0,
      "end_time": 308570.0,
      "text": "and I got this consultancy position with the World Bank Africa Region."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308735.0,
      "end_time": 311491.0,
      "text": "And so I remember one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311515.0,
      "end_time": 316163.0,
      "text": "my boss -- we were having a conversation on some project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 316187.0,
      "end_time": 319228.0,
      "text": "and he mentioned a particular World Bank project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319252.0,
      "end_time": 324224.0,
      "text": "a large-scale irrigation project that cost millions of dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 324248.0,
      "end_time": 325579.0,
      "text": "in Niger Republic"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 325603.0,
      "end_time": 328877.0,
      "text": "that was faltering sustainably."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328901.0,
      "end_time": 331244.0,
      "text": "He said this project wasn&#39;t so sustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331268.0,
      "end_time": 335491.0,
      "text": "and it bothered those that instituted the whole package."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 336350.0,
      "end_time": 338824.0,
      "text": "But then he mentioned a particular project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 339517.0,
      "end_time": 344433.0,
      "text": "a particular traditional irrigation method that was hugely successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344458.0,
      "end_time": 348155.0,
      "text": "in the same Niger Republic where the World Bank project was failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 348930.0,
      "end_time": 350426.0,
      "text": "And that got me thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 351281.0,
      "end_time": 353240.0,
      "text": "So I did further research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 353984.0,
      "end_time": 356369.0,
      "text": "and I found out about Tassa."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 357775.0,
      "end_time": 361544.0,
      "text": "Tassa is a traditional irrigation method"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361569.0,
      "end_time": 367762.0,
      "text": "where 20- to 30-centimeter-wide and 20- to 30-centimeter-deep holes"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 367786.0,
      "end_time": 370660.0,
      "text": "are dug across a field to be cultivated."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 371220.0,
      "end_time": 375333.0,
      "text": "Then, a small dam is constructed around the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376296.0,
      "end_time": 379921.0,
      "text": "and then crops are planted across the surface area."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 379946.0,
      "end_time": 383250.0,
      "text": "What happens is that when rain falls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 383274.0,
      "end_time": 386258.0,
      "text": "the holes are able to store the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 386282.0,
      "end_time": 390990.0,
      "text": "and appropriate it to the extent that the plant needs the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390124.0,
      "end_time": 393390.0,
      "text": "The plant can only assimilate as much water as needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393414.0,
      "end_time": 394984.0,
      "text": "until harvest time."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 396582.0,
      "end_time": 400275.0,
      "text": "Niger is 75 percent scorched desert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 400299.0,
      "end_time": 402991.0,
      "text": "so this is something that is a life-or-death situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 403160.0,
      "end_time": 404824.0,
      "text": "and it has been used for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 405384.0,
      "end_time": 407486.0,
      "text": "In an experiment that was conducted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408233.0,
      "end_time": 413646.0,
      "text": "two similar plots of land were used in the experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 413670.0,
      "end_time": 416301.0,
      "text": "and one plot of land"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 416325.0,
      "end_time": 418267.0,
      "text": "did not have the Tassa technique on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 418291.0,
      "end_time": 419457.0,
      "text": "Similar plots."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419482.0,
      "end_time": 422640.0,
      "text": "The other one had Tassa technique constructed on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423332.0,
      "end_time": 427870.0,
      "text": "Then similar grains of millet also were planted on both plots."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 428450.0,
      "end_time": 430252.0,
      "text": "During harvest time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 430276.0,
      "end_time": 433428.0,
      "text": "the plot of land without Tassa technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 433452.0,
      "end_time": 437623.0,
      "text": "yielded 11 kilograms of millet per hectare."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 438737.0,
      "end_time": 441320.0,
      "text": "The plot of land with Tassa technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 441560.0,
      "end_time": 446909.0,
      "text": "yielded 553 kilograms of millet per hectare."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 447660.0,
      "end_time": 450245.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 450269.0,
      "end_time": 454182.0,
      "text": "I looked at the research, and I looked at myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 454206.0,
      "end_time": 457458.0,
      "text": "I said, \"I studied agriculture for 12 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 457482.0,
      "end_time": 460892.0,
      "text": "from primary to Senior Six, as we say in East Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 460916.0,
      "end_time": 463262.0,
      "text": "SS3 in West Africa or 12th grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 463286.0,
      "end_time": 464943.0,
      "text": "No one ever taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 464967.0,
      "end_time": 468772.0,
      "text": "of any form of traditional African knowledge of cultivation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 468797.0,
      "end_time": 470591.0,
      "text": "of harvesting, of anything --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 470615.0,
      "end_time": 474443.0,
      "text": "that will work in modern times and actually succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 474467.0,
      "end_time": 479680.0,
      "text": "where something imported from the West would struggle to succeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 479775.0,
      "end_time": 482888.0,
      "text": "That was when I knew the challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 482912.0,
      "end_time": 485491.0,
      "text": "the challenge of Africa&#39;s curricula,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 485649.0,
      "end_time": 490447.0,
      "text": "And I thus began my quest to dedicate my life, concern my life work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 490471.0,
      "end_time": 494763.0,
      "text": "to studying, conducting research on Africa&#39;s own knowledge system"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 494787.0,
      "end_time": 497787.0,
      "text": "and being able to advocate for its mainstreaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 497811.0,
      "end_time": 500657.0,
      "text": "in education, in research, policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 500682.0,
      "end_time": 502737.0,
      "text": "across sectors and industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 503445.0,
      "end_time": 507289.0,
      "text": "Another conversation and experience I had at the bank"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 507313.0,
      "end_time": 512630.0,
      "text": "I guess made me take that final decision of where I was going to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 512870.0,
      "end_time": 516111.0,
      "text": "even though it wasn&#39;t the most lucrative research to go into,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 516135.0,
      "end_time": 518452.0,
      "text": "but it was just about what I believed in."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 518937.0,
      "end_time": 523563.0,
      "text": "And so one day, my boss said that he likes to go to Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 523587.0,
      "end_time": 528122.0,
      "text": "to negotiate World Bank loans and to work on World Bank projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 528614.0,
      "end_time": 530563.0,
      "text": "And I was intrigued. I asked him why."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 530587.0,
      "end_time": 533330.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Oh, when I go to Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 533570.0,
      "end_time": 534766.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s so easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 535255.0,
      "end_time": 539913.0,
      "text": "I just write up my loan documents and my project proposal in Washington, DC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 539937.0,
      "end_time": 542890.0,
      "text": "I go to Africa, and they all just get signed."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 542914.0,
      "end_time": 546302.0,
      "text": "I get the best deal, and I&#39;m back to base."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 546326.0,
      "end_time": 548533.0,
      "text": "My bosses are happy with me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 548933.0,
      "end_time": 552620.0,
      "text": "But then he said, \"I hate going to Asia or ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 552644.0,
      "end_time": 556870.0,
      "text": "and he mentioned a particular country, Asia and some of these countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 556111.0,
      "end_time": 560134.0,
      "text": "\"They keep me for this, trying to get the best deal for their countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 560158.0,
      "end_time": 561334.0,
      "text": "They get the best deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 561358.0,
      "end_time": 564266.0,
      "text": "They tell me, &#39;Oh, that clause will not work for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 564290.0,
      "end_time": 565896.0,
      "text": "in our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 565921.0,
      "end_time": 568894.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not our reality. It&#39;s just so Western.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 568918.0,
      "end_time": 572290.0,
      "text": "And they tell me, &#39;Oh, we have enough experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 572530.0,
      "end_time": 573256.0,
      "text": "to take care of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 573280.0,
      "end_time": 574901.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have enough experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 574925.0,
      "end_time": 576780.0,
      "text": "We know our aim.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 576102.0,
      "end_time": 578547.0,
      "text": "And they just keep going through all these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 578571.0,
      "end_time": 581910.0,
      "text": "By the time they finish, yes, they get the best deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 581115.0,
      "end_time": 584280.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m so exhausted and I don&#39;t get the best deal for the bank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 584304.0,
      "end_time": 585483.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re in business.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 585507.0,
      "end_time": 587301.0,
      "text": "\"Really?\" I thought in my head, \"OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 587326.0,
      "end_time": 591606.0,
      "text": "I was privileged to sit in on a loan negotiating session"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 591630.0,
      "end_time": 593295.0,
      "text": "in an African country."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 593319.0,
      "end_time": 596139.0,
      "text": "So I would do these consultancy positions during summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 596163.0,
      "end_time": 598847.0,
      "text": "you know, since I was a doctoral student."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 598871.0,
      "end_time": 603203.0,
      "text": "And then I traveled with the team, with the World Bank team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 603227.0,
      "end_time": 607543.0,
      "text": "as more like someone to help out with organizational matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 607567.0,
      "end_time": 610834.0,
      "text": "But I sat in during the negotiating session."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 611730.0,
      "end_time": 616662.0,
      "text": "I had mostly Euro-Americans, you know, with me from Washington, DC."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 616686.0,
      "end_time": 621536.0,
      "text": "And I looked across the table at my African brothers and sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 621993.0,
      "end_time": 624327.0,
      "text": "I could see intimidation on their faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 624771.0,
      "end_time": 627340.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t believe they had anything to offer"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 627580.0,
      "end_time": 629346.0,
      "text": "the great-great-grandchildren of Mungo Park --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 629370.0,
      "end_time": 631987.0,
      "text": "the owners of \"apple\" in \"A is for apple.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 632110.0,
      "end_time": 634786.0,
      "text": "They just sat and watched: \"Oh, just give us, let us sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 634811.0,
      "end_time": 636724.0,
      "text": "You own the knowledge. You know it all."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 636748.0,
      "end_time": 638957.0,
      "text": "Just, where do we sign? Show us, let us sign.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 638981.0,
      "end_time": 642160.0,
      "text": "They had no voice. They didn&#39;t believe in themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 646544.0,
      "end_time": 647727.0,
      "text": "Excuse me."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 648587.0,
      "end_time": 649759.0,
      "text": "And so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 651212.0,
      "end_time": 653538.0,
      "text": "I have been doing this for a decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 653562.0,
      "end_time": 657600.0,
      "text": "I have been conducting research on Africa&#39;s knowledge system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 657300.0,
      "end_time": 659274.0,
      "text": "original, authentic, traditional knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 659298.0,
      "end_time": 662495.0,
      "text": "In the few cases where this has been implemented in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 662519.0,
      "end_time": 665300.0,
      "text": "there has been remarkable successes recorded."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 665270.0,
      "end_time": 666564.0,
      "text": "I think of Gacaca."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 667256.0,
      "end_time": 671988.0,
      "text": "Gacaca is Rwanda&#39;s traditional judicial system"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 672120.0,
      "end_time": 674106.0,
      "text": "that was used after the genocide."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 674130.0,
      "end_time": 676561.0,
      "text": "In 1994, when the genocide ended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 678100.0,
      "end_time": 680662.0,
      "text": "Rwanda&#39;s national court system was in shambles:"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 680686.0,
      "end_time": 686212.0,
      "text": "no judges, no lawyers to try hundreds of thousands of genocide cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 686236.0,
      "end_time": 689744.0,
      "text": "So the government of Rwanda came up with this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 689768.0,
      "end_time": 693163.0,
      "text": "to resuscitate a traditional judicial system known as Gacaca."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 693625.0,
      "end_time": 697720.0,
      "text": "Gacaca is a community-based judicial system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 697960.0,
      "end_time": 700330.0,
      "text": "where community members come together"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 700570.0,
      "end_time": 703806.0,
      "text": "to elect men and women of proven integrity"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 703830.0,
      "end_time": 708340.0,
      "text": "to try cases of crimes committed within these communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 709255.0,
      "end_time": 714732.0,
      "text": "So by the time Gacaca concluded its trial of genocide cases in 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 715619.0,
      "end_time": 722594.0,
      "text": "12,000 community-based courts had tried approximately 1.2 million cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 723334.0,
      "end_time": 724685.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a record."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 725169.0,
      "end_time": 730150.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 730438.0,
      "end_time": 736380.0,
      "text": "Most importantly is that Gacaca emphasized Rwanda&#39;s traditional philosophy"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 736620.0,
      "end_time": 739155.0,
      "text": "of reconciliation and reintegration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 739179.0,
      "end_time": 743570.0,
      "text": "as against the whole punitive and banishment idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 743810.0,
      "end_time": 746803.0,
      "text": "that undergirds present-day Western style."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 747481.0,
      "end_time": 751376.0,
      "text": "And not to compare, but just to say that it really emphasized"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 751400.0,
      "end_time": 754754.0,
      "text": "Rwanda&#39;s traditional method of philosophy."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 755269.0,
      "end_time": 757866.0,
      "text": "And so it was Mwalimu Julius Nyerere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 757890.0,
      "end_time": 759631.0,
      "text": "former president of Tanzania --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 759655.0,
      "end_time": 761131.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 761155.0,
      "end_time": 764331.0,
      "text": "who said that you cannot develop people."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 764916.0,
      "end_time": 767974.0,
      "text": "People will have to develop themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 768563.0,
      "end_time": 769948.0,
      "text": "I agree with Mwalimu."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 770487.0,
      "end_time": 771875.0,
      "text": "I am convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 771899.0,
      "end_time": 775522.0,
      "text": "that Africa&#39;s further transformation, Africa&#39;s advancement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 775546.0,
      "end_time": 780325.0,
      "text": "rests simply in the acknowledgment, validation and mainstreaming"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 780349.0,
      "end_time": 785338.0,
      "text": "of Africa&#39;s own traditional, authentic, original, indigenous knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 785362.0,
      "end_time": 790233.0,
      "text": "in education, in research, in policy making and across sectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 790816.0,
      "end_time": 793333.0,
      "text": "This is not going to be easy for Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 793357.0,
      "end_time": 796821.0,
      "text": "It is not going to be easy for a people used to being told how to think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 796845.0,
      "end_time": 799210.0,
      "text": "what to do, how to go about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 799234.0,
      "end_time": 802388.0,
      "text": "a people long subjected to the intellectual guidance"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 802412.0,
      "end_time": 804154.0,
      "text": "and direction of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 804178.0,
      "end_time": 805845.0,
      "text": "be they the colonial masters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 805869.0,
      "end_time": 808841.0,
      "text": "aid industry or international news media."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 808865.0,
      "end_time": 812990.0,
      "text": "But it is a task that we have to do to make progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 812123.0,
      "end_time": 815230.0,
      "text": "I am strengthened by the words of Joseph Shabalala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 815470.0,
      "end_time": 818521.0,
      "text": "founder of the South African choral group Ladysmith Black Mambazo."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 818545.0,
      "end_time": 824232.0,
      "text": "He said that the task ahead of us can never, ever be greater"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 824256.0,
      "end_time": 826409.0,
      "text": "than the power within us."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 826433.0,
      "end_time": 827591.0,
      "text": "We can do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 827615.0,
      "end_time": 830175.0,
      "text": "We can unlearn looking down on ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 830199.0,
      "end_time": 834394.0,
      "text": "We can learn to place value on our reality and our knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 834418.0,
      "end_time": 835573.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 835597.0,
      "end_time": 837680.0,
      "text": "(Swahili) Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 837920.0,
      "end_time": 838615.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 838639.0,
      "end_time": 840841.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 840865.0,
      "end_time": 845564.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}